{"tid":2278461,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"中美電影節 | 甄子丹鄭秀文稱帝封后 《葉問4》成大贏家","createTime":"2020-11-09T07:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T07:26:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6043c076e962a78e4e8b9b46fc907df28a8a0265","tid":2278461,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:26:57.000Z","msg":"因為疫情關係，第16屆中美電影節取消頒獎典禮，大會今早在網上公佈結果。甄子丹和鄭秀文（Sammi）分別在頒獎禮中稱帝封后，Sammi主演的電影《聖荷西謀殺案》不但獲頒金天使獎電影，她也奪得最佳女主角獎，Sammi跟佟大為扮演兩夫妻，因為蔡卓妍的探訪，揭發了這對夫婦背後隱藏的身份。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201109/77SNVCPNNFCHZODA7PN53KSER4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201109%2F77SNVCPNNFCHZODA7PN53KSER4%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=4cc46208\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201109%2F77SNVCPNNFCHZODA7PN53KSER4%2F&h=4afc12bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201109/77SNVCPNNFCHZODA7PN53KSER4/</a>"}]}